measurements.description: Three flowers and four buds on one 64-cm upright unsupported inflorescence; dorsal sepal recurved, light chartreuse, darker centrally and basally, darker veins; synsepal ovate-epiculate, recurved centrally, cream, striped light green; petals spatulate, pale chartreuse, lighter distally; pouch light chartreuse; staminode light chartreuse, darker centrally; substance medium; texture matte, pouch waxy.
